WEBVTT

00:10:29.160 --> 00:10:31.736
which will allow them
to see who our friends are,

00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:32.976
what we say

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:35.720
and even to impersonate us online.

00:10:36.520 --> 00:10:39.176
Now, civil libertarians like myself

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:43.336
have been trying to draw
people's attention to these things

00:10:43.360 --> 00:10:45.936
and fighting against them for years.

00:10:45.960 --> 00:10:50.160
This was a huge problem
during the Obama administration,

00:10:50.960 --> 00:10:53.240
but now the problem is worse.

00:10:54.520 --> 00:10:56.976
When the New York Police Department

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:58.696
spies on Muslims

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:02.576
or a police department
uses license plate detectors